        "meta_description": "Alistair Owen is the author of Smoking in Bed: Conversations with Bruce Robinson (one of DavidHare’s Books of the Year in the Guardian), Story and Character: Interviews with British Screenwriters,Hampton on Hampton (one of Craig Raine’s Books of the Year in the Observer), The Art of ScreenAdaptation: Top Writers Reveal Their Craft and The Mirror and the Road: Conversations with WilliamBoyd.",
